[src:mesa-graphics-stack/free-and-open-source-graphics-device-driver] The Linux graphics stack has evolved, detoured by the X Window System core protocol.
[src:mesa-graphics-stack/free-and-open-source-graphics-device-driver] AMD's proprietary driver, AMD Catalyst for their Radeon, is available for Microsoft Windows and Linux (formerly fglrx).
